Available Tools: send_push | send_bulk_push | get_push_status | cancel_push
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "user_id": "string", "title": "string", "body": "string", "data": {}, "device_token": "string" }
Response Schema: { "notification_id": "string", "status": "sent|delivered|failed", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Distribute a bulk alert to all Android users about the upcoming winter holiday schedule.
Call: { "func_call": "send_bulk_push", "user_id": "hr_notify_bot", "title": "Holiday Office Hours", "body": "Our offices will be closed from Dec 24 to Jan 2. Emergency support remains available.", "data": { "holiday_id": "WIN-2024", "region": "global", "platform": "android" }, "device_token": "*" }
Response: { "notification_id": "blk_hol_88776655", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2024-12-20T08:15:00Z" }

